    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit boasts a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS system and has had the rod bearing service completed to ensure internal longevity. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, feeding power to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the rear subframe mounting points reinforced as a proactive measure. The factory suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing fresh bushings and dampers to maintain the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in a deep Carbon Black with pristine Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering for the serious collector.",
